      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont want to risk a hypoglycemic episode while i sleep... if i take it and my sugar is already low from not eating i could pass out. wouldnt it be smarter and safer to just skip the shot tonight and start fresh in the morning? it seems like the logical way to avoid a crash.",
